abstract: omg : dean unglert is reportedly dating ` bachelor ' alum lesley murphy !
article: after stirring up all kinds of drama on bachelor in paradise with a headline-making love triangle last fall and admitting to `` a lot of bad decisions , '' the bachelorette 's dean unglert has reportedly found love again -- with yet another the bachelor contestant ! though neither party has confirmed the news , e! , us weekly , and several other sites are reporting that unglert is cozying up to former bachelor contestant lesley murphy , who appeared on season 17 of the show to fight for the affections of sean lowe . as you may recall , murphy also recently underwent breast implant surgery following a double mastectomy in april to prevent breast cancer as a carrier of the brca 2 gene .

the pair , who first met while filming next month 's the bachelor : winter games spinoff , were reportedly spotted together at the sundance film festival in park city , utah on friday , holding hands and getting cozy . according to e! , the lovebirds are indeed in an exclusive relationship , but were supposed to be keeping their romance under wraps so as not to spoil the show 's plot . the bachelor : winter games will premiere on february 13th at 8 pm est on abc and is made up of four episodes hosted by trista and ryan sutter .

cast members from all around the world , including japan , australia , and canada , will be appearing , as well as us faves ben higgins and ashley iaconetti . current bachelor arie luyendyk jr. . is also slated to make an appearance , as are rachel lindsay and jojo fletcher . we 'll definitely be tuning in , if only to get the full scoop on dean and lesley ! will you be watching bachelor : winter games ? tweet us @britandco . you might also likenick viall and vanessa grimaldi have no plans to rush down the aisle arie luyendyk jr. .
